Dept. of Computer Science<br>
226 Withers Hall<br>
N.C. State University<br>
Raleigh, NC 27695-8206 USA<br>
<p>
(919) 515-7862 (voice)<br>
(919) 515-7896 (fax)<br>
<p>
Email: <a href="mailto:rance@csc.ncsu.edu">rance@csc.ncsu.edu</a>
<p>
Daniel Jackson<br>
School of Computer Science<br>
Carnegie Mellon University<br>
5000 Forbes Avenue<br>
Pittsburgh, PA 15213 USA<br>
<p>
(412) 268-5143  (voice)<br>
(412) 268-5576 (fax)<br>
<p>
Email: <a href="mailto:dnj@cs.cmu.edu">dnj@cs.cmu.edu</a>
<p>
<hr>
<p>
