<Title>Developing High Assurance Building Blocks</Title>
<H2>DEVELOPING HIGH ASSURANCE BUILDING BLOCKS</h2>
<HR>
<p>
This page is part of the web at the
<a href="../index.html">
 Center for High Assurance Computer Systems</a>.
<p>
<HR>

<H2>Mission</H2>

Developing new approaches, including the use of formal
specifications and automated reasoning tools, for designing,
implementing, and verifying software/hardware building blocks that can
be certified to enforce specified critical properties with a high
degree of assurance.

<H2>Contributors</H2>

<ul>
  <li> <a href="../personnel/moore.html">
        Andrew P. Moore</a>, Principal Investigator
  <li> <a href="../personnel/landwehr.html">
        Carl E. Landwehr</a>
</ul>

<a href="../publications/CHACS/DHABBindex.html">
 <H2>Publications</H2></a>


<HR>
<p>
<ADDRESS>
Developing High Assurance Building Blocks / Andrew Moore / moore@itd.nrl.navy.mil 
</ADDRESS>
