<Title>Secure Information Through Replicated Architecture</Title>

<h2>SECURE INFORMATION THROUGH REPLICATED ARCHITECTURE</h2>

<HR>
<p>
This page is part of the web at the
<a href="../index.html">
 Center for High Assurance Computer Systems</a>.
<p>
<HR>

<H2>Mission</H2>

Explore physical separation and data replication as
a practical approach to multilevel secure database systems and
information systems generally.

<a href="../gifs/SIN_Proto.html">
 Here</a> is our prototype, and
<a href="../gifs/SIN_sol.html">
 here</a> is our solution for distributed systems.

