<TITLE>Cipher bad e-mail address list</TITLE>
<H2>Cipher bad e-mail address list</H2>
<p>
Addresses in the list below have been deleted from the 
Cipher e-mail distribution list 
because the mail could not go through for
one reason or another, including: bad format, host/user unknown, 
undeliverable because mailbox consistently full or 
over quota, loops in delivery.  If you know of a correction,
please send it to <i>cipher-request@itd.nrl.navy.mil</i>. 
