<p>
On the information warfare front, a Washington Technology Online article
by Neil Munro reports that U.S. Attorney General Janet Reno asked in
a March 14 memo that cabinet members create a national cyberspace defense
"entity" and establish a cyberwar defense policy task force.  The task
force, headed by a private sector presidential appointee and including
