<LI> <A NAME="tex2html1355" HREF="node35.html#SECTION02314000000000000000">Synchronous Communication</A>
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html1356" HREF="node36.html#SECTION02315000000000000000">Non-Divergent Processes</A>
</UL>
