</UL> 
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html2023" HREF="node83.html#SECTION03230000000000000000">Justification of the Get Design</A>
<UL> 
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html2024" HREF="node84.html#SECTION03231000000000000000">Assertions Argument</A>
