<BR> <P>
<H2><A NAME="SECTION03222000000000000000">Outchar design</A></H2>
<P>
<TT>Outchar</TT> receives the final delimiter and checks the parity of
the character.  If the final delimiter is <TT>stopbit</TT> and the
character is of even parity, the non-delimited character is
transmitted over <TT>mid</TT>.
<P>
<P>
<A NAME="maclab62">&#160;</A>
<B>&lt;</B><I>Outchar design</I><B>&gt;</B><B>[</B>62<B>]</B><A NAME=9748>&#160;</A><B>M</B><B>=</B> <BR><TT>&nbsp;</TT> <TT>procedure&nbsp;Outchar&nbsp;(mvar&nbsp;st&nbsp;:&nbsp;</TT>
<B>&lt;</B><I>State type</I><B>&gt;</B><B>[</B><A HREF="node150.html#maclab159">159</A><B>]</B><A NAME=9759>&#160;</A> <TT>,<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;lvar&nbsp;chr&nbsp;:&nbsp;</TT>
<B>&lt;</B><I>Buffer type</I><B>&gt;</B><B>[</B><A HREF="node149.html#maclab137">137</A><B>]</B><A NAME=9768>&#160;</A> <TT>,<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;lvar&nbsp;chsz&nbsp;:&nbsp;int,<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;lvar&nbsp;tick&nbsp;:&nbsp;</TT>
<B>&lt;</B><I>Event type</I><B>&gt;</B><B>[</B><A HREF="node150.html#maclab161">161</A><B>]</B><A NAME=9777>&#160;</A> <TT>,<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pvar&nbsp;cntdwn&nbsp;:&nbsp;int)&nbsp;=<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TT>
<B>&lt;</B><I>Outchar specification</I><B>&gt;</B><B>[</B><A HREF="node92.html#maclab76">76</A><B>]</B><A NAME=9786>&#160;</A> <TT></TT><TT><BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;begin<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pvar&nbsp;b&nbsp;:&nbsp;</TT>
<B>&lt;</B><I>Bit type</I><B>&gt;</B><B>[</B><A HREF="node149.html#maclab139">139</A><B>]</B><A NAME=9795>&#160;</A> <TT></TT><TT><BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pvar&nbsp;is_odd&nbsp;:&nbsp;bool<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TT>
<B>&lt;</B><I>inbit ? b</I><B>&gt;</B><B>[</B><A HREF="node150.html#maclab170">170</A><B>]</B><A NAME=9804>&#160;</A> <TT></TT><TT><BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;odd_parity_check(</TT>
<B>&lt;</B><I>tail of chr</I><B>&gt;</B><B>[</B><A HREF="node149.html#maclab153">153</A><B>]</B><A NAME=9813>&#160;</A> <TT>,is_odd)<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cntdwn&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;0<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and&nbsp;not&nbsp;is_odd<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and&nbsp;</TT>
<B>&lt;</B><I>b is stopbit</I><B>&gt;</B><B>[</B><A HREF="node149.html#maclab149">149</A><B>]</B><A NAME=9822>&#160;</A> <TT>&nbsp;then<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TT>
<B>&lt;</B><I>mid ! tail of chr</I><B>&gt;</B><B>[</B><A HREF="node150.html#maclab179">179</A><B>]</B><A NAME=9831>&#160;</A> <TT></TT><TT><BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;end&nbsp;if<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;end&nbsp;Outchar;</TT>
<P>
This macro is invoked in definition <A HREF="node176.html#maclab209">209</A>.<P>
