<H1><A NAME="SECTION03330000000000000000">Justification of the Put Design</A></H1>
<P>
<A NAME="JustificationofthePutDesign">&#160;</A>
<P>
This section presents an intuitive justification that the design of
<TT>Put</TT> satisfies the assertions of <TT>Put</TT> described in
Chapter&nbsp;<A HREF="node30.html#CriticalRequirementsSpecification">4</A>.  More specifically,
we must show that the requirements listed in Section&nbsp;<A HREF="node60.html#SummaryoftheLogicalArchitectureCriticalRequirements">5.4</A> follow from the design
of <TT>Put</TT> described in the last section.
<P>
<BR> <HR>
