<BR> <P>
<H2><A NAME="SECTION04131000000000000000">Assumptions</A></H2>
<P>
<DL COMPACT><DT><STRONG>1</STRONG>
<DD> Power is continuously supplied to <TT>Rptr</TT>.
  <DT><STRONG>2.1P</STRONG>
<DD> The environment does not send data over <TT>outbit</TT>,
           <TT>err1</TT>, or <TT>err2</TT>.
  <DT><STRONG>3.1P</STRONG>
<DD> The environment does not send or receive data over
           <TT>data1</TT> or <TT>data2</TT>.
<P>
 </DL><BR> <HR>
