<H1><A NAME="SECTION04200000000000000000">Repeater Detailed Physical Design</A></H1>
<P>
<A NAME="RepeaterDetailedPhysicalDesign">&#160;</A>
<P>
This chapter describes the <TT>Rptr</TT> CSP process implementation in FDR
and the justification that this physical design satisfies the critical
requirements identified in the last chapter.  This justification
generates a set of critical requirements that must be satisfied of any
further refinement of <TT>Rptr</TT>.
<P>
<BR> <HR>
<UL> 
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html2605" HREF="node120.html#SECTION04210000000000000000">Formal Specification of the Physical Design</A>
