<UL> 
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html2612" HREF="node127.html#SECTION04222100000000000000">Assert 1:</A>
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html2613" HREF="node128.html#SECTION04222200000000000000">Assert 2:</A>
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html2614" HREF="node129.html#SECTION04222300000000000000">Assert 3:</A>
