<H1><A NAME="SECTION04230000000000000000">Summary of the Implementation Critical Requirements</A></H1>
<P>
<A NAME="SummaryoftheImplementationCriticalRequirements">&#160;</A>
<P>
The following assumptions must be validated of any environment in which
<TT>Rptr</TT> is embedded.  The following assertions must be proven of any
refinement of the <TT>Rptr</TT> physical design.
<P>
<BR> <HR>
<UL> 
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html2847" HREF="node137.html#SECTION04231000000000000000">Assumptions</A>
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html2848" HREF="node138.html#SECTION04232000000000000000">Assertions</A>
<UL> 
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html2849" HREF="node139.html#SECTION04232100000000000000">Informal Assertions</A>
</UL>
</UL>
