') <TT>&gt;.<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else&nbsp;hist(st)=hist(st_0)&nbsp;end&nbsp;if;</TT>
<P>
This macro is invoked in definitions <A HREF="node168.html#maclab193">193</A> and <A HREF="node169.html#maclab195">195</A>.<P>
