<BR> <P>
<H1><A NAME="SECTION05420000000000000000">CSP Library</A></H1>
<P>
<A NAME="CSPLibrary">&#160;</A>
<P>
The library containing the extensions to EVES to allow specification
and verification of CSP processes using the Traces Refinement model contains the
following units.  This library is documented fully in
[<A HREF="node155.html#MooreEVES94">21</A>].
<P>
<DL ><DT><STRONG>nset</STRONG>
<DD> -- a theory of finite sets containing up to five elements
<P>
   <DT><STRONG>tr</STRONG>
<DD> -- a theory of traces (or sequences) of some object
<P>
   <DT><STRONG>pr</STRONG>
<DD> -- a theory of a subset of the CSP processes
<P>
   <DT><STRONG>fpt</STRONG>
<DD> -- a theory of parameterized recursive processes
<P>
   <DT><STRONG>reqs</STRONG>
<DD> -- a theory of CSP alphabets and trace specifications
<P>
 </DL><BR> <HR>
<P><ADDRESS>
<I>Andy Moore <BR>
Tue Aug 20 13:26:31 EDT 1996</I>
</ADDRESS>
</BODY>
