&nbsp;&nbsp;end&nbsp;in_char_set_is_trace;<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;induct&nbsp;char_set_help&nbsp;(c,&nbsp;chsz);<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;with&nbsp;enabled&nbsp;(pr!map_tack'definition)&nbsp;reduce;<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;prenex;<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;equality&nbsp;substitute;<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;rewrite;<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;</TT><TT><BR>
