&nbsp;&nbsp;with&nbsp;disabled&nbsp;(tr!append)&nbsp;reduce;<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;split&nbsp;chsz&nbsp;=&nbsp;(len&nbsp;.&lt;&gt;.);<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;simplify;<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;rewrite;<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;</TT><TT><BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;make&nbsp;cseq&nbsp;model;<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;</TT><TT><BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TT>
<P>
This macro is invoked in definitions <A HREF="node154.html#maclab185">185</A> and <A HREF="node172.html#maclab200">200</A>.<P>
